img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個公仔好唔開心，同我去佢到上堂一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T06:24:13.000Z","msg":"上堂之前咪咁嘅樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />落咗堂就會好開心，好似地獄又折返人間咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc1c299573a5da5055f8089b54247cb21e34fee6","tid":2454241,"uid":367224,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T06:24:50.000Z","msg":"細個聽人講學公文數 以為好似奧數咁係一種數學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3279173a9c79d714de53080a724d73bfb4ae312b","tid":2454241,"uid":34884,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"4bb0eda753ca6cedd0cbf2f752de74a93b52abae","tid":2454241,"uid":147737,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T06:03:05.000Z","msg":"竟然無人讀過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T06:26:39.000Z","msg":"同你一樣，小五小六被老母捉咗去補英數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n堂堂都畀幾十條數你做，Pass到就上一級，Fail幾次就落返下一級<br />\n試過小六上到中二Linear Equation，但完全唔知做緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，英文填充直頭亂寫<br />\n剩係知錯/低分就會畀啲TA屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一直都喺呢啲level停留<br />\n<br />\n後尾同屋企人講如果我數學有進步就可以唔使補<br />\n因為我提早接觸中二數，所以成績有進步唔使再補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中三計下計下反而覺得計數幾得意，數學成績直頭衝上全級頭十，可以揀M2<br />\n<br />\n呢個經歷令我明白到讀書尤其中小學最重要係學習動機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇學習動機，點填鴨都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反有學習動機就會自己上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fca426b7b11866cb9199ee0bf1cae06fd9c38c0","tid":2454241,"uid":121245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T06:30:59.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後中學咪又係撳cal 機<br />\n手計得快有咩用 又唔係教奧數啲思維"},{"pid":"253349b021318384591f88687f5d9a5b0aedcbbc","tid":2454241,"uid":147737,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"3279173a9c79d714de53080a724d73bfb4ae312b","tid":2454241,"uid":34884,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"4bb0eda753ca6cedd0cbf2f752de74a93b52abae","tid":2454241,"uid":147737,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T06:03:05.000Z","msg":"竟然無人讀過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T06:26:39.000Z","msg":"同你一樣，小五小六被老母捉咗去補英數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n堂堂都畀幾十條數你做，Pass到就上一級，Fail幾次就落返下一級<br />\n試過小六上到中二Linear Equation，但完全唔知做緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，英文填充直頭亂寫<br />\n剩係知錯/低分就會畀啲TA屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一直都喺呢啲level停留<br />\n<br />\n後尾同屋企人講如果我數學有進步就可以唔使補<br />\n因為我提早接觸中二數，所以成績有進步唔使再補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中三計下計下反而覺得計數幾得意，數學成績直頭衝上全級頭十，可以揀M2<br />\n<br />\n呢個經歷令我明白到讀書尤其中小學最重要係學習動機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇學習動機，點填鴨都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反有學習動機就會自己上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T06:34:42.000Z","msg":"Me too<br />\n我都係中三中四對數學有興趣，會特登理解d公式點derive,之後dse輕鬆攞星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後諗返就知kumon最多係令你計數叻，但唔係數學叻"},{"pid":"a43071529ea9e07c6dbf38bfc1bc3e5b8b2eccc1","tid":2454241,"uid":147737,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"6fca426b7b11866cb9199ee0bf1cae06fd9c38c0","tid":2454241,"uid":121245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T06:30:59.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後中學咪又係撳cal 機<br />\n手計得快有咩用 又唔係教奧數啲思維"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T06:38:50.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n果時好記得個ta一句:你寫直式計最少都10秒，我依個方法就兩秒計到<br />\n而家諗返真係得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌，個答案咪一樣咁多分<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />去到用計數機，大家都係咁快添<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a0db72c415f91d0e3096b64b6dbabddc1ea0dac","tid":2454241,"uid":30524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T06:39:54.000Z","msg":"小學讀左4年，係咁做加減乘除<br />\n無撚聊到<br />\n印象又冇教過我乜野<br />\n只係上堂做數，返屋企又做數<br />\n個時係用工字繩穿起D練習，唔知而家係咪<br />\n做到躁逐張搣出黎摺飛機飛落街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一堂派4-5份功課，每份功課少咁一兩張，加埋都少左成份LOL"},{"pid":"ca6865e4dcd10dba84223dc27bf0e53f7570717f","tid":2454241,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9df7a269c427715434256d086e60a512e9c6abd","tid":2454241,"uid":147737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"89f34efc1a3908372dd83b9a97c52701c0bb3e56","tid":2454241,"uid":555,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T06:06:13.000Z","msg":"操到數學好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T06:09:27.000Z","msg":"應付到小學數學既，中學就差d<br />\n數學始終理解先係上策"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T06:45:53.000Z","msg":"個底好咗好多 做中學數都易上手"},{"pid":"955b6ffd87a6e868ebe85493c2122d8bb4cb94dd","tid":2454241,"uid":85205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T06:47:16.000Z","msg":"小學阿媽逼我去，cls做到我喊，好大陰影好大壓力<br />\n<br />\n阿媽都有逼我家姐去，家姐話細個嗰陣個老師會擺個計時器係佢前面，限時內要做哂啲數，個計時器先會停，做唔哂個計時器會響到勁大聲，個個望過黎<br />\n細個面皮薄，呢啲情況會好驚好尷尬<br />\n<br />\nKumon填鴨式教育真係好變態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b1568f12883d4ef21fd34775601156b661fd2c4","tid":2454241,"uid":147737,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3a0db72c415f91d0e3096b64b6dbabddc1ea0dac","tid":2454241,"uid":30524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T06:39:54.000Z","msg":"小學讀左4年，係咁做加減乘除<br />\n無撚聊到<br />\n印象又冇教過我乜野<br />\n只係上堂做數，返屋企又做數<br />\n個時係用工字繩穿起D練習，唔知而家係咪<br />\n做到躁逐張搣出黎摺飛機飛落街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一堂派4-5份功課，每份功課少咁一兩張，加埋都少左成份LOL"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T06:51:54.000Z","msg":"我做嘅時候都係同你一樣模式<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />工字繩真係回憶嚟，同埋我記得張紙係細細張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰時心諗俾吓呢啲功課咁就收錢，我求其塞幾個數字落去出幾題都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9f5a3f7fb81e548a7e031bfbdb0c640e6d843dd","tid":2454241,"uid":45094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T06:54:08.000Z","msg":"我以前中英數都做過<br />\n中文真係最撚冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}